name: SEED
description: From a Telegram Miniapp with over 60M users, SEED is evolving into the top RPG in Web3 gaming, inspired by the success of games like Pokémon Go and Axie Infinity. Leveraging the power of VR, AI, and seamless messenger-based onboarding, SEED not only ensures mass accessibility but also creates an engaging and interconnected gaming universe. Beyond its flagship game, SEED’s vision extends further. Together with the SUI Foundation, we will support a durable ecosystem of games and applications through the SEED Combinator Program for startups, creating a self-sustaining Web3 ecosystem.
